headline: 1 Software Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 to Brush Off
summary: Software is eating the world, and virtually no business is left untouched by it. Companies bringing it to life have been rewarded with explosive earnings growth and high valuation multiples, but the latter has weighed on returns as the industry was flat over the past six months. A consolation is that the S&P 500 hasn’t budged either.
